aran, Peru (1995) Science, 269, pp. 48-50; Wilby, R.L., O'Hare, G., Barnsley, N., The North Atlantic Oscillation and British Isles climate variability, 1865-1996 (1997) Weather, 52, pp. 266-275","Pepin, N.; Department of Geography, University of Portsmouth, Lion Terrace, Portsmouth, Hants PO1 3HE, United Kingdom",,,,,,,,0177798X,,,,"English","Theor. Appl. Climatol.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0035094067
